title: Frank Lloyd Wright Saguaro Folding Backpack
description:
Backpack converts into a pouch, unzip the pouch, and unpack a backpack with two zipper compartments and adjustable shoulder straps. Perfect for travel, with a quick release clip for easy attachment to luggage or travel bag. Strong and lightweight, this backpack can handle up to 30 lbs.  The design is adapted from a series of 12 abstracts Wright created for the covers of Liberty Magazine from 1926 to 1928. Made of recycled polyester blend.

14 x 12 x 4 in.

Backpack in pouch 6 x 4 x 1 1/2  in.
